Privacy Policy for Tangle Logic Game

Effective Date: 20/07/2025

Thank you for choosing to play Tangle Logic Game. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information from users of Tangle Logic Game.

2. Advertising
Tangle Logic Game displays third-party advertisements to support the free version of the game. These ads may be provided by services such as Google AdMob or other ad networks, which may use device identifiers and cookies to serve relevant ads.

Please refer to their privacy policies for more details:

Google AdMob Privacy Policy

These services may collect:

Device information (e.g., device type, operating system)

Non-personal usage data

We do not have access to or store this information ourselves.

3. Children's Privacy
Tangle Logic Game is suitable for users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect or solicit any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13 (or applicable age in your jurisdiction).

4. Data Security
As we do not collect user data, there is no personal information to protect. However, we rely on secure and reputable third-party services for advertising.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with a revised "Effective Date."

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:
